{"tid":868531,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[好多大戰]2018-19 LIHKG香港女神總會盃第二圈抽籤結果暨比賽日期公佈","createTime":"2018-10-19T14:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T09:14:04.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1bad52faf5e16640cca6e3cb5802fcb86406773d","tid":868531,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=syaji7nkk8Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dsyaji7nkk8Y&d=BpnPxQCMLZFFl5rQmDXvrS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=0ed0ccda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=syaji7nkk8Y</a><br />\n抽籤片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二圈共24場賽事將於11月17及18日兩天舉行<br />\n*(超)=該女神今季於超聯作賽 (冠)=該女神今季於冠聯作賽<br />\n(甲)=該女神今季於甲組作賽 (乙)=該女神今季於乙組作賽<br />\n(非)=該女神今季未於任何聯賽中作賽<br />\n<br />\n2018-11-17 凌晨十二點開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n陳靜(非)vs劉穎鏇(冠)<br />\n陳自瑤(甲)vs衛詩雅(乙)<br />\n趙希洛(非)vs莊錠欣(冠)<br />\n鄭宇澄(乙)vs譚凱琪(非)<br />\n李蔓瑩(非)vs陳庭欣(冠)<br />\n陳敏(甲)vs林穎彤(乙)<br />\n陳煒(冠)vs朱智賢(甲)<br />\n黃心穎(冠)vs何依婷(乙)<br />\n龔嘉欣(乙)vs陳潔玲(甲)<br />\n湯唯(非)vs王敏奕(甲)<br />\n孫慧雪(冠)vs陳華鑫(乙)<br />\n劉佩玥(甲)vs趙慧珊@SG(冠)<br />\n<br />\n2018-11-18 凌晨十二點開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n陳嘉倩(超)vs岑麗香(冠)<br />\n姚子羚(甲)vs鄺潔楹(乙)<br />\n陳嘉靖(非)vs林泳淘(冠)<br />\n林凱恩(乙)vs黃翠如(冠)<br />\n彭慧中(冠)vs袁澧林(冠)<br />\n黃智雯(冠)vs呂慧儀(非)<br />\n李施嬅(冠)vs陳穎欣@SG(超)<br />\n朱晨麗(冠)vs楊偲泳(非)<br />\n吳嘉熙@SG(甲)vs何超蓮(乙)<br />\n曾淑雅(非)vs陳嘉寶(冠)<br />\n游蕙禎(冠)vs湯怡(冠)<br />\n周秀娜(非)vs湯洛雯(甲)<br />\n<br />\n希望巴絲們到時踴躍參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0395f0ea54f026f0c9a3bb38efa070a62d63cd","tid":868531,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:22:28.000Z","msg":"陳靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f34a7f4ab5d9cfbe38